title: Denver McKee (1960) Bonanza Western Classic TV

sources.title: Denver McKee (1960) Bonanza Western Classic TV
sources.description:
Retired U.S. Deputy Marshall Denver McKee (Franchot Tone) is willing to do anything to make his daughter (Natalie Trundy) happy. Bob Barker guest stars.
 
Director: Jacques Tourneur
Writers: Fred Freiberger, Steve McNeil
Stars: Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
